title: East Oceanfront Dining
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in Blockade Runner Beach Resort in the tropical oceanfront gardens, this is a seafood restaurant that also caters to vegans, vegetarians, raw, and gluten-intolerant--just let your server know about your diet. Offers a Meatless Monday menu on the first Monday of every month.
